milestones.description: Wettimuny and Fernando's 71-run partnership is SL's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 55 between Wettimuny and Fernando
This is the lowest match aggregate (337) involving teams Australia & Sri Lanka in ODIs
Guy de Alwis has broken the record for most dismissals (6) in ODIs for SL, going past Mahes Goonatilleke's 4
Guy de Alwis has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (5) in ODIs for SL, going past Mahes Goonatilleke's 2
